  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large, heavy pot or Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the lardons and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the carrots and zucchini and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the lamb, cumin, coriander, cinnamon, paprika, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute, stirring to combine.",
    "Add the panang curry paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring to combine.",
    "Add the chicken broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Cover the pot and transfer to the oven. Braise the tagine for 1 hour and 15 minutes, or until the lamb is tender.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot."
  ],
